text: Ywathit () is a town in Mohnyin Township in Kachin State of Myanmar. It is on the road between Hopin and Indawgyi Lake. ==External links== *"Ywathit Map — Satellite Images of Ywathit" Maplandia.com Category:Township capitals of Myanmar Category:Populated places in Kachin State
title: Ywathit, Kachin State
